metadata.name: Seoul Trace
metadata.description:
ChristopheJr - A Self Titled Collection

Title: Seoul Trace  
Artist: Christopher W Howell  
Edition: 1/1  
Medium: Digital Photography  
Location: Seoul, South Korea  
https:\ChristopheJr.io

A night training flight, dedicated to a review of the procedures of the Prohibited Area Trace named P-73, brought me the opportunity to capture this moment in time. At 800 ft, along the Han River, we flew the required route along the trace to validate our understanding of its boarder. The nights fog, the lack of illumination from the moon, gave me this opportunity to capture and share. A moment out of the cockpit of our helicopter on the Seoul Trace.
